pageContext.claim: “In Ohio, where we had a crowd like this, and outside there were thousands and thousands of people. And then we went to Indiana, where we had a crowd like this, and there were thousands and thousands of people outside.”
pageContext.analysis: Twitter users at the Ohio event found that the crowd did not fill the venue. While Trump was speaking, four people were in front of a TV screen set up outside the venue, according to a photo taken by a Twitter user at the event. In Indiana, reporters at this event found no people waiting outside.
